Adventist education is a vital and influential ministry that reaches and transforms the lives of children worldwide for Jesus. 

Upon observing low academic achievement among their students, teachers in the South Pacific Division began to engage their students in Bible study. As a result, many witnessed remarkable improvements in their studentsâ€™ academic performance!
